                <h2><b>KIDNEY</b></h2>
                <u><b>Functions</b></u>
                <li>Filtration of waste products from the blood</li>
                <li>Tabular reabsorption of useful substances from the filtrate</li>
                <li>Tabular secretion of unwanted substances back into the collection ducts</li>
                <li>Maintaining normal blood pressure by balancing electrolytes in the blood</li><br>
                <u><b>Failures</b></u>
                <li>Diabetes</li>
                <li>Infection</li>
                <li>High blood pressure</li>
                <li>Inflammation(Nephritis)</li>
                <li>Kidney stones prostate enlargement,etc</li>
            </div>
