                <h2><b>HEART</b></h2>
            <u><b>Functions</b></u>
            <li>Generating blood pressure</li>
            <li>Routing blood</li>
            <li>Ensuring one-way blood flow</li>
            <li>Regulating blood supply</li>
            <li>Supplying oxygen and nutrients to tissues</li>
            <li>Transport of hormone to cells</li><br><br>
            <u><b>Failures</b></u>
            <li>High blood pressure </li>
            <li>Valve defects</li>
            <li>Coronoray heart disease</li>
            <li>Alcohol or drug misuse</li>
            <li>Lung problems</li>
