            <u><b>Functions</b></u>
            <li>Break down all categories of food</li>
            <li>Regulates blood sugar</li>
            <li>Blood sugar level is crucial to the functioning of key organs including the brain liver and kidneys</li>
            <li>Correct chemicals in the proper quantities</li>
            <li>That produces enzymes for digestion</li><br><br>
            <u><b>Failures</b></u>
            <li>Autoimmune disease</li>
            <li>Drinking lots of alcohol</li>
            <li>Infection</li>
            <li>Metabolic disorders</li>
            <li>Medications</li>
