            <u><b>Functions</b></u>
            <li>immunity against infection</li>
            <li>Factory for proteins and cholesterol</li>
            <li>Excretes wastes via bile</li>
            <li>Regulate blood clotting</li>
            <li>Clears blood of drugs,chemicals,alcohol</li>
            <li>Excretes bile for fat digestion</li><br>
            <u><b>Failure</b></u>
            <li>Chronic alcohol abuse</li>
            <li>Over dosage of medicines</li>
            <li>Fatty liver</li>
            <li>Infections</li>
            <li>Breaks down nutrients from foods</li>
        </div>
