                        <h2><b>BLOOD</b></h2>
                        <u><b>You can give blood if:</b></u>
                        <li>You are fit and healthy</li>
                        <li>You are aged 18-65</li>
                        <li>You weigh more than 45kg</li>
                        <li>It's been more than 6 months since you got a tattoo</li>
                        <li>You take blood pressure medication and your blood pressure is stable </li><br>
                        <u><b>You can't give blood if:</b></u>
                        <li>You are under the influence of alcohol</li>
                        <li>You are taking antibiotics</li>
                        <li>You are pregnant and breastfeeding</li>
                        <li>You have a cold or flu</li>
                        <li>You have ever injected a recreational drug</li>
